{"tid":2208834,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解游極都返唔到上岸？認識離岸流","createTime":"2020-09-19T08:18:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-22T15:12:23.000Z","uid":11598,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"774331c081c929126baaeb5a31fd1104e633601b","tid":2208834,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:18:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/6/6d/Backcomp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F6%2F6d%2FBackcomp.gif&h=6d0e4b72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n間中會見到有新聞報道有泳客喺岸邊游水體力不支遇溺，點解明明咁近岸邊都會浸親？<br />\n原來海浪衝上岸之後失去勢能而會返回海入邊，但因為後浪推前浪<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n剛衝上岸嘅海水會積聚喺岸邊，大量嘅海水會湧去比較深水嘅區域衝返入海<br />\n形成離岸嘅水流，足以將人推離岸邊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以體力不支遇溺好大可能係因為遇上離岸流 無論你點游 <br />\n強大嘅水流會繼續將你沖離岸邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/fan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢條片介紹咗點樣識別離岸流同佢哋有咩特徵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PuAlDTC_gIQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DPuAlDTC_gIQ&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCvno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=a612472f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=PuAlDTC_gIQ</a><br />\n<br />\n我都係而家先知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中小學教科書好似無講過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dfd0363dd0c3574bc5df3cff4d5de0ab99a4093","tid":2208834,"uid":59832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T08:19:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d94a31d33e11f4e26aedb0bfd16e9d5cae75bd1","t